<plot>Interviews with actual Pearl Harbor survivors and cast and filmmakers show us how terrible the surprise attack was, and how difficult it was to create the film. This is not entirely a making-of Pearl Harbor (2001), just peoples memories, video from the film and images from December 7, 1941.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?279993</url></doc>
